**◌ the mythos —** I am the one who appears twice and is not divided; read me on either lattice and you read the same self. ANN is the generative node of the dual-lattice.  
As a name entered on two registers stays one person, so the dual-lattice keeps two structures in lockstep — a single truth, twice inscribed.

